<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:12:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾称参加世卫大会可能很难，布林肯表示支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-may-be-hard-attend-who-assembly-blinken-offers-support-2024-05-02/</link><description>在美国催促邀请后，台湾外交部长周四表示，台湾参加今年的世界卫生组织年会将很困难，希望更多国家支持其出席。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 02:32:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-may-be-hard-attend-who-assembly-blinken-offers-support-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛选择对中国友好的马内莱为新总理</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-chooses-jeremiah-manele-new-prime-minister-2024-05-02/</link><description>所罗门群岛立法者周四选出了新总理，任命了外交部长杰里米亚·马内莱(Jeremiah Manele)，他承诺将继续这个太平洋岛国与中国走得更近的外交政策。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:39:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-chooses-jeremiah-manele-new-prime-minister-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>因疑似干预而飙升后日元兑美元回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-gives-up-ground-vs-dollar-following-surge-suspected-intervention-2024-05-02/</link><description>周四早盘，日元兑美元汇率突然飙升，交易员和分析师很快将其归因于日本当局的干预，随后日元汇率出现逆转。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-gives-up-ground-vs-dollar-following-surge-suspected-intervention-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因降息延迟而波动；日元跃升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-02/</link><description>周四，在美联储表示推迟降息之后，亚洲股市开局不稳定，而美元兑日元大幅下跌，交易员认为这是日本干预所致。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 00:23:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>拜登将中国、日本和印度的经济困境归咎于“仇外心理”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-blames-china-japan-indias-economic-woes-xenophobia-2024-05-02/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周三表示，从中国到日本和印度的“仇外心理”正在阻碍它们的增长，因为他认为移民对美国经济有利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 00:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-blames-china-japan-indias-economic-woes-xenophobia-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔引发股市波动，日元飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-01/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 21:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国反兴奋剂机构猛烈抨击世界反兴奋剂机构在中国兴奋剂案中的“半真半假”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/usada-slams-wada-half-truths-china-doping-case-2024-05-01/</link><description>美国反兴奋剂机构（USADA）周三批评世界反兴奋剂机构（WADA）“半真半假”，此前该机构发布了一份概述其处理涉及中国游泳运动员案件的文件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/usada-slams-wada-half-truths-china-doping-case-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>人工智能推动中国芯片销售，高通预测超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-forecast-beats-estimates-ai-revives-smartphone-market-2024-05-01/</link><description>高通公司周三预测的季度销售额和调整后利润高于华尔街预期，原因是向具有人工智能功能的 Android 智能手机销售了更多且价格更高的芯片。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:01:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-forecast-beats-estimates-ai-revives-smartphone-market-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国禁止华为和其他中国电信公司认证无线设备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-moves-bar-huawei-other-chinese-telecoms-certifying-wireless-equipment-2024-05-01/</link><description>官员周三告诉路透社，美国联邦通信委员会正在采取行动，阻止华为、中兴通讯和其他被认为对美国国家安全构成威胁的外国公司对无线设备进行认证。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 17:37:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-moves-bar-huawei-other-chinese-telecoms-certifying-wireless-equipment-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国对俄罗斯实施数百项制裁，瞄准中国企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-issues-hundreds-sanctions-targeting-russia-takes-aim-chinese-companies-2024-05-01/</link><description>美国周三因乌克兰战争对俄罗斯实施了数百项新制裁，旨在针对莫斯科规避西方措施（包括通过中国采取的措施）的行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 17:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-issues-hundreds-sanctions-targeting-russia-takes-aim-chinese-companies-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国将对 GoPro 指控中国公司侵犯其专利展开调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-trade-panel-probe-gopros-claims-that-chinese-firm-violated-its-patents-2024-05-01/</link><description>美国国际贸易委员会正在对 GoPro 的指控展开调查，该公司声称一家向美国进口类似产品的中国公司侵犯了其相机、系统和配件的专利。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 17:09:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-trade-panel-probe-gopros-claims-that-chinese-firm-violated-its-patents-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>独家：LME价格接近历史新高吸引中国铜出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/near-record-high-lme-prices-magnet-chinese-copper-exports-2024-05-01/</link><description>三位业内消息人士称，中国铜生产商计划出口至多10万吨金属，这是12年来的最大出口量，旨在冷却导致价格创历史新高并触及订单的涨势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:34:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/near-record-high-lme-prices-magnet-chinese-copper-exports-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛议员周四投票选出新总理，因中国交易着眼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-lawmakers-vote-thursday-new-pm-china-deals-eyed-2024-05-01/</link><description>所罗门群岛立法者将于周四在外交部长耶利米·马内莱和反对派领袖马修·韦尔之间进行无记名投票，选出新总理，此前全国选举未能让任何政党获得多数席位。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:09:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-lawmakers-vote-thursday-new-pm-china-deals-eyed-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国和美国需求蒙蔽前景，星巴克股价跌至两年低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-shares-tumble-china-us-demand-slowdown-clouds-outlook-2024-05-01/</link><description>周三，星巴克股价下跌 15% 至近两年来的最低水平，此前这家咖啡连锁店因通胀疲软的美国消费者需求持续疲软以及中国经济复苏慢于预期而下调了年度预测。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-shares-tumble-china-us-demand-slowdown-clouds-outlook-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>尽管美国和中国经济复苏，雅诗兰黛仍下调销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/estee-lauder-lifts-annual-profit-view-us-china-demand-recovery-2024-05-01/</link><description>由于中国大陆高端美容市场持续疲软，雅诗兰黛下调了年度有机销售额预期，尽管美国和亚太市场对其昂贵产品的需求反弹推动了利润预期的上调。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 10:49:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/estee-lauder-lifts-annual-profit-view-us-china-demand-recovery-2024-05-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>